msgctxt "80_Saejima"
msgid "(He's gone. Was that the thief? Sure is a quick sumbitch.)"
msgstr "(Se escapó. ¿Ese era el ladrón? Vaya, qué rápido es ese cabrón)"

msgctxt "92_Saejima"
msgid "(Ah, well. I'll put somethin' else by the manhole and wait for him to make another appearance.)"
msgstr "(Bueno, pondré algo más junto a la alcantarilla y esperaré a que vuelva a aparecer)."

